<HEADLINE> Halle Berry Fined For Leaving Scene  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   BEVERLY HILLS, Calif. (AP) -- Actress Halle Berry was fined
$13,500 and placed on three years' probation after pleading no
contest to leaving the scene of an accident.
</P>
<P>
   ''Your honor, I would like the court to know that I have taken
this matter very seriously from the very beginning. I am pleased
that this can be resolved,'' Berry, 31, said in court Wednesday.
</P>
