<HEADLINE> Fla-Mich St. To Play Next 2 Seasons  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   GAINESVILLE, Fla. (AP) -- Florida and Michigan State agreed
Thursday to meet next season in a rematch of last month's national
championship game.
</P>
<P>
   As part of a two-year contract, the Gators will play the
Spartans in East Lansing on Dec. 6. Michigan State will play at
Florida in the 2001-02 season.
</P>
<P>
   Michigan State defeated Florida 89-76 in Indianapolis on April 3
to win its second national championship.
</P>
<P>
   The only other meeting between the schools was Florida's 83-59
victory on Dec. 30, 1987.
</P>
